title: More FAKE reviews...
review: It's pathetic how all these reviews giving it 9's and 10's are from accounts that have literally never reviewed or rated any other film. What's that tell you?? Low budget garbage. Period.

title: Amateurish
review: If you are used to watching proper movies you might not want to bother with this.

title: Boring Boring Boring
review: I didn't make it to the end as it's a very boring and repetitive film. There is still room for a mockumentary as This Country has proved, but you need far better writing and acting than this.
